#: realmember.php:571
msgid "🌐 Nickname Frequency in the Fediverse"
msgstr "🌐 Nickname Frequency in the Fediverse"

#: realmember.php:572
msgid "Spammers often register the same nickname on many servers in parallel. RealMember therefore counts how often a user's nickname already occurs in your federated contact database (table <code>contact</code>) — i.e., how often Friendica already knows this handle from the Fediverse."
msgstr "Spammers often register the same nickname on many servers in parallel. RealMember therefore counts how often a user's nickname already occurs in your federated contact database (table <code>contact</code>) — i.e., how often Friendica already knows this handle from the Fediverse."

#: realmember.php:573
msgid "💡 This check is read-only, does not write anything to the database, and uses only data that Friendica already knows through normal federation."
msgstr "💡 This check is read-only, does not write anything to the database, and uses only data that Friendica already knows through normal federation."

